Detailed Description

GPS measurement data set element.

This structure contains a GPS measurement data set element. This structure is based on OMA-TS-ULP V1.0.

Field Documentation

U32 RXN_GPSMsrSetElement_t::gpsTOW

TOW in the format matching the GPSTOW24b format within Nav Data messages (see ICD-200)

RXN_GPSMsrElement_t RXN_GPSMsrSetElement_t::MsrList[16]

Measurement Element List. Alloc may not be in place for 16 entries. Check numEntries!

U08 RXN_GPSMsrSetElement_t::numEntries

Number of entries in MsrList. Range 1 - 16.

U32 RXN_GPSMsrSetElement_t::refFrame

Reference Frame. Range 0 - 42431.
